{"slideshow_credits": null, "snippet": "At 63, the influential TriBeCa chef will shut Bouley and reopen it in a smaller space with a mission of health.", "abstract": "David Bouley announces he will temporarily close Bouley, 30-year-old restaurant that is part of his TriBeCa dining empire, to take 18-month sabbatical; plans to intensely study connection between food and health by taking classes and consulting with experts around world; is set to reopen Bouley afterwards with new mission to optimize health by offering tasting menus that address medical and dietary concerns. ", "section_name": "Food", "print_page": "1", "document_type": "article", "byline": {"person": [{"firstname": "Jeff", "role": "reported", "lastname": "GORDINIER", "rank": 1, "organization": ""}], "original": "By JEFF GORDINIER"}, "web_url": "http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/08/dining/david-bouley-restaurants-tribeca.html", "lead_paragraph": "At 63, the influential TriBeCa chef will shut Bouley and reopen it in a smaller space with a mission of health.", "headline": {"main": "David Bouley Plans to Retool His Restaurants, and Himself", "print_headline": "The Wizard Retools His Lab"}, "_id": "5756efb738f0d8514b3cec0f", "word_count": "1753", "multimedia": [{"height": 126, "url": "images/2016/06/08/dining/08BOULEY1-WEB/08BOULEY1-WEB-thumbWide.jpg", "legacy": {"wideheight": "126", "wide": "images/2016/06/08/dining/08BOULEY1-WEB/08BOULEY1-WEB-thumbWide.jpg", "widewidth": "190"}, "subtype": "wide", "width": 190, "type": "image"}, {"height": 480, "url": "images/2016/06/08/dining/08BOULEY1-WEB/08BOULEY1-WEB-articleLarge.jpg", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2016/06/08/dining/08BOULEY1-WEB/08BOULEY1-WEB-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": "600", "xlargeheight": "480"}, "subtype": "xlarge", "width": 600, "type": "image"}, {"height": 75, "url": "images/2016/06/08/dining/08BOULEY1-WEB/08BOULEY1-WEB-thumbStandard.jpg", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2016/06/08/dining/08BOULEY1-WEB/08BOULEY1-WEB-thumbStandard.jpg", "thu